    <p>Same Day Appliance Repair has certified LG technicians across Los Angeles County, Orange County, and Ventura County. When you call before noon, we typically arrive the same day — usually within 1 to 1.5 hours. We carry OEM heating elements in our vans for the most common LG models, so 85% of repairs are completed on the first visit.</p>

